    The Best Reasons to Choose the Civic Sedan

    Take a Closer Look

    View detailed interior and exterior photos before you schedule your test drive.
    BROWSE GALLERY

    Civic Sedan vs. the Competition

    See how the Civic Sedan stacks up against the competition, feature by feature.
    COMPARE NOW

    A Memorable Impression

    The 2018 Civic Sedan features aggressive lines and refined features that make it stand out from the crowd.
    Light Up the Night

    Civic Sedan Touring features LED Headlights with Auto-On/Off that are perfect for lighting up the road and your life.

    Stylish Sedan

    With a bold, aggressive face and sharp, sophisticated body lines throughout, every angle of the Civic Sedan exterior is the right angle.

    Sharp and Sleek

    Civic Sedan features a sleek profile and a long wheelbase, making it sporty even when standing still. 

    Stop and “C”

    The "C"-shaped LED Taillights were designed to make a strong styling statement that's uniquely Civic. 

    The Right Stance

    The wide, aggressive stance shows that Civic Sedan is ready to scorch the pavement.

    Honda Genuine Accessories

    Make the outside of your Civic Sedan as unique as you with Honda Genuine Accessories. There are plenty of ways to individualize your Civic Sedan.

    Door Visors

    Enjoy some fresh air, even when the weather isn't ideal, with Door Visors.

    Decklid Spoiler

    The Decklid Spoiler adds a subtle, tasteful enhancement that makes a big contribution to the sleek aerodynamic appearance of your Civic Sedan.

    Splash Guard Set

    Splash Guards are a nice finishing touch. They give your Civic Sedan a great look and help protect your paint from chips and stains.

    Inside Outstanding

    Civic Sedan has grown up, and features the most comfortable and sophisticated interior of any Civic ever.
    Cockpit Confidence

    Commencing launch sequence in 3... 2... 1... Blast off in the confidence-inspiring cockpit of the Civic Sedan.

    All On Display

    The design-centric instrument panel features a single-level display that’s easy to read so you can spend more time watching the scenery fly by.

    Everything Within Reach

    Everything is in reach of the driver — from the controls to the storage console, which fits drinks, a tablet or a small bag.

    Electric Parking Brake

    No more pulling on a brake lever. Civic Sedan features a segment-first Electric Parking Brake that activates with the lift of a finger.

    Sit in Style

    Civic Sedan offers three cloth and three leather interiors, each bringing its own sophisticated flair to the cockpit.

    Heat Things Up

    Civic Sedan offers heated seats for the driver and front passenger. Touring models also add heating for outboard rear passengers.

    In the Power Seat

    Getting comfy is easy with the 8-Way Power Driver’s Seat, which includes a lower cushion that tilts up and down to get your seat position just right.

    The Lap of Luxury

    Civic Sedan features luxe leather details throughout the cabin, including Leather-Trimmed Seats and a Leather-Wrapped Steering Wheel and Shift Knob.

    Cloth standard on LX, EX and EX-T. Leather standard on EX-L and Touring.

    Room in the Rear

    With 60/40 Split Fold-Down Rear Seats and a spacious trunk, Civic Sedan offers plenty of cargo options — from picking up groceries to setting out for a long weekend.*

    Fun for Five

    Civic Sedan has seating for five and all the interior space you’ll need to pile in with your friends and turn a Sunday drive into something bigger.

    Pack It In

    With up to 15.1 cu. ft. of cargo space, 60/40 Split Fold-Down Rear Seats and a trunk pass-through for longer objects, you have plenty of room to pack it all in and head on out.*

    All-Season Floor Mats

    Wet boots. Muddy shoes. Dog hair. No problem. All-Season Floor Mats act as a protective layer between nature and your original carpets.*

    Illuminated Console

    Bring to light the refined details of the Civic Sedan interior with the soft blue glow of Console Illumination.

    Interior Illumination

    Interior Illumination provides an upscale and aesthetically pleasing touch to your interior with a soft glow of light in the driver and passenger footwells.

    The Sophisticated Civic

    Performance

    With up to 174 horsepower*, a fully independent suspension and two choices of transmissions, Civic Sedan was designed with performance in mind.

    Take The Turbo

    Civic Sedan offers a turbocharged engine that produces 174 horsepower* and turns every green light into a reason to put the pedal down.

    Fun and Efficient

    Civic Sedan comes standard with a 158-horsepower*, 2.0-liter normally-aspirated engine that helped it receive an EPA 40 MPG HWY rating*, proving normal is anything but boring.

    Handle the Curves

    Civic Sedan was designed to handle with the best of them, featuring standard MacPherson struts.

    6-Speed Excitement

    Becoming one with Civic Sedan is easy once you grab the stick shift and make your way through its snappy, 6-Speed Manual Transmission.

    Civic CVT

    The Continuously Variable Transmissions (CVT) offered for Civic Sedan were optimized to match each available engine, for plenty of power without sacrificing fuel efficiency.

    174 hp standard on EX-T, EX-L and Touring.

    Technology

    Civic Sedan is packed with cutting-edge-technology offerings and perfectly primed for leading the charge for the next generation.

    Be Aware of What's Behind

    Get a better view of what's behind you with a Multi-Angle Rearview Camera* that offers three different views: normal, top-down and wide.

    Know The Way

    Be your own navigator and get to wherever you want to go with the available Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System™.*

    Honda LaneWatch™

    With Honda LaneWatch™*, changing lanes is now easier. Just signal right, and live video displays from a small camera on your passenger-side mirror.

    No Wires. No Worries.

    Leave your cables and wires at home. An accessory wireless charging mat is the better way to charge your compatible smartphone.

    Plug In and Play

    A USB Audio Interface* comes standard so you can plug in and control your compatible digital devices while also charging them.

    Connected Audio

    With an available 450-Watt, 10-Speaker Premium Audio System, Pandora® compatibility, HondaLink® and more, Civic Sedan keeps you well connected.

    The Connected Civic

    Listen to your music, talk shows, audio books and news with available SiriusXM®* Radio, HD Radio™* and Pandora®* compatibility.

    CarPlay® All Day

    Tap into your iPhone® and get directions, send or receive messages and access your music library all through the Display Audio Touch-Screen.*

    Google on the Go

    Use your compatible Android™ phone to access directions, text messages and your music library, all through the Display Audio Touch-Screen.*

    The Synced Sedan

    Connecting your compatible mobile device is seamless with HondaLink®, making it easy to stream music, receive vehicle notifications and even schedule service appointments.*

    450-Watt Premium Audio System standard on Touring.

    Honda Sensing®

    This suite of safety and driver-assistive technologies is designed to alert you to things you might miss while driving.

    Honda Sensing® available on LX, EX, EX-T and EX-L. Standard on Touring.

    Collision Mitigation Braking System™ (CMBS™)

    Helps brake the vehicle when it senses an otherwise unavoidable collision with a vehicle detected in front of you.*

      Road Departure Mitigation System (RDM)

      A small camera sees road markers, alerts you if you’re about to leave the road, and can take action to help keep you from doing so.*

        Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow

        Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow helps you maintain a set following-interval on the highway, so you don't have to manually change your speed.*

          Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS)

          If your vehicle begins to stray from the center of a detected lane without signaling, the steering adjusts to help bring you back to the lane center.*

            Accelerated Smarts. Absurd Fun.

            A quick-shifting 6-Speed Manual Transmission. An aggressive, angular body. That bold, red badge. It can mean only one thing — the legendary Civic Si is here.

            17-inch Accessory Alloy Wheels with Tires

            $1,646*

            The perfect way to add extra wow factor to your new Civic. Alloy wheels not only look amazing, but they can also help ensure the longevity of wheel bearings and suspension joints.

            • Wheels are stringently tested to match all Honda requirements as well as those from the Society of Automotive Engineers
            • Hub-centric design ensures an exact fit for wheel balance and less vibration to ensure a smooth ride
            • Width-matched to fit your car precisely for proper clearance and handling
            • Clear-coat finish over the front of the wheels helps prevent corrosion and makes cleaning easier


            Requires Tire 17-in (P215/50R17) Firestone

            Prices shown are manufacturer suggested retail prices only. Installation cost for accessories is not included. Dealer costs may vary. Prices exclude applicable taxes.
